comment.author: 41018061@N02
comment._content: With great respect to those who put the "official" nickname on this machine, I believe it is not the Fairey Long Range Monoplane, but rather the Fairey Jet Gyrodyne - built from the second prototype of the Fairey FB-1 Gyrodyne - which provided some data towards the better known Rotodyne project.
